                "type": "output_text",
                "text": "To compute the shipping cost, I will use the formula provided in the shipping-cost-skill:\n\n**Formula:**  \nShipping Cost = Base Cost + (Cost per kg × Weight)\n\nFor domestic shipping:\n- Base Cost = $5\n- Cost per kg = $2\n\nGiven:\n- Weight = 3 kg\n\n**Calculation:**\nShipping Cost = $5 + ($2 × 3)  \nShipping Cost = $5 + $6  \nShipping Cost = $11\n\n**Final Answer:**  \nThe shipping cost for a 3 kg package shipped domestically is **$11**.",
